<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6245898>
    dc:description "FIGURE 36. Oniphenes bicoloratus gen. et sp. nov., orig. A–H: holotype, male and I: paratype, female from QLD (“… 3 km ENE of Mt. Tozer …”); A: body, dorsal; B: head, dorsal; C: head and thorax, ventral; D: lateral side of abdominal segments 5 and 6, dorsal; E: male anal sclerite, ventral; F: tegmen, ventral; G: penis trunk, dorsal; H: proximal part of inner sac with armature; I: ovipositor, ventral. Scale bars: a = 0.5 mm to Fig. A; b = 0.5 mm to Figs B–D; с = 0.25 mm to Figs E–I." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6245898/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6245906>
    dc:description "FIGURE 38. Oniphenes subunicolor gen. et sp. nov., orig. A–H: holotype, male from QLD (“… Cape Tribulation area, 1–11 May 1992 …”) and I: paratype, female from QLD (“Bellenden Ker Range …”); A: body, dorsal; B: head, dorsal; C: head and thorax, ventral; D: lateral side of abdominal segments 5 and 6, dorsal; E: male anal sclerite and spiculum gastrale, ventral; F: tegmen, ventral; G: penis trunk, dorsal; H: ovipositor, ventral. Scale bars: a = 0.5 mm to Fig. A; b = 0.5 mm to Figs B–D; с = 0.25 mm to Figs E–I." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6245906/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6245902>
    dc:description "FIGURE 37. Oniphenes lobanovi gen. et sp. nov., orig. A–D: paratype, female from QLD (“… Cape Tribulation area, 21–28 Mar. 1984 …”), E–H: holotype, male from QLD (“Cairns”) and I: paratype, female from QLD (“… Cape Tribulation area, 1–11 May 1992 …”); A: body, dorsal; B: head, dorsal; C: head and thorax, ventral; D: lateral side of abdominal segments 5 and 6, dorsal; E: male anal sclerite and spiculum gastrale, ventral; F: tegmen, ventral; G: penis trunk, dorsal; H: proximal part of inner sac with armature; I: ovipositor, ventral. Scale bars: a = 0.5 mm to Fig. A; b = 0.5 mm to Figs B–D; с = 0.25 mm to Figs E–I." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6245902/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

